Pre-Depends:    debconf (>= 1.4.30) | debconf-2.0
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - NQRustBackup Recovery Imager (Barri) command line tool
 NQRustBackup is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides the NQRustBackup Recovery Imager (Barri) command line tool (barri-cli)
